headline: We're back for the Spring 2017 semester! Our first meeting will be in about two weeks on Wednesday, February 1st with our sponsor Cisco at 7PM in GDC 5.302 (not the basement!). We'll also have a Mobile Security talk at MADCON, the student developer conference hosted by MAD, on Saturday, February 4th. More details will be available as we get closer to the event date.
